Sales and virtual system documentation



Architecture
Layered development and exception handling. The layer structure of the back end system will be as shown picture


Implementation:
Implementation of the following conceptual model.
Instance Conceptual Model Diagram



Technologies:
Java 8
Rest with SpringBoot 2
H2 memory database
JPA
Maven


Link Data Base:

http://localhost:8080/h2-console/

Retrieve the data and make it available through a Rest API. The following end points must be made available:
 
Endpoints
/ categorias / {id} Category and its products
/ clientes / {id} Customer, their phones and addresses
/ pedidos / {id} Order, your customer, your payment, your order items, your shipping address